post.body: It's a destination, but there's two to choose from - mine and @edacherry's.
Sounds to me like your outfit is complete.
The only thing left would be the dramatic prairie dog.
Yikes! Glad you're all okay. Next time tell the median you're famous.
Andrew WK tells me it's time to party.
Latest issue of Decibel, V8, Daily-C, owl jammies, circle bed, Spaz, the internet, and a book of crime scenes. Being sick isn't all bad.
If the bathroom in Proz's in Devil's Lake taught me anything, it's that Kenny is kind of a slut, and sweater boy is gay.
I resolve to listen to your resolutions.
If I were on House Hunters I'd tell them that I really need a space to be on the internet.
Catching up after 5 days off the grid is overwhelming.
Load car, unload car. Rinse repeat until end of time. Hello, again, Minnesota.
Oh man, what is that? Is that... ? A warm feeling about something? Geez, that's weird.
Watching @s4xton's animated twitvatar, because what else am I going to do?
There is pie everywhere.
My iPod is on Foo Fighters Overdrive. Get it?
Stuffing 529 envelopes is a lot like that dream where you're running towards a door and it never gets closer.
Company Logo of the day: "Green's Construction. Pound With Pride!"
St Paul declares snow emergency. Website says, "Normal parking rules apply." Not falling for that.
There's a good chance that @chuckumentary needs a vacation day.
Pretty excited for JCVD tonight at Lagoon. Oh yes.
